      "text": "The square is a knot of footpaths and half-finished plans. A watchful guard holds a casual line near the gate. A scholar lingers by a shaded wall with notes in hand. A merchant's stall glints with small, useful things. Beyond the last buildings, a rough track leads toward quiet country.",
